****Font Collections****


****Using font-family****
-->Common to see sans-serif

****Font Selection****
body{
    font-family:Ariel, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}
    -->If the first choice isn't available on a particular browser, 
        it will go down the list until it finds one that is

****Font Styling***


****Text Properties****
-->We can change many aspects about the way a text element looks
-text-indent
-letter-spacing
-word-spacing
-text-decoration
-etc.